781
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,700
Come on, talk to me.

782
00:42:34,860 --> 00:42:35,860
It's going to rain again.

783
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:36,780
Well...

784
00:42:37,060 --> 00:42:37,900
This awful weather.

785
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:39,620
Always changing.

786
00:42:59,260 --> 00:43:00,380
Mao!

787
00:43:00,940 --> 00:43:03,500
I'm sorry!

788
00:43:20,420 --> 00:43:22,700
Mao!

789
00:43:44,380 --> 00:43:47,740
[Loyalty]

790
00:43:48,020 --> 00:43:49,980
[Brotherhood]

791
00:44:56,860 --> 00:45:00,740
♪The brightest star in the evening sky♪

792
00:45:01,100 --> 00:45:05,380
♪I still recall the dream
I chased so high♪

